This browser extension was developed to effortlessly extract files and attachments from PDF documents. You have the option to either download all files or selectively choose specific ones for download.

ЁЯЪА  Main Features:
тЬЕ Extract all files and attachments from PDFs and display them in a list.
тЬЕ Convenient one-click download for all files.
тЬЕ Flexibility to download specific files as needed.

Is it Free?
тЬФя╕П Absolutely! You can fully utilize the basic functionality for free, and there is also the option to upgrade for additional features.
